### Loading
- `DeckConfig.fromFile` → `rootBundle.loadString('assets/deck_config.yaml')` (`yaml_config_parser.dart` in `flutter_base_05`)
- `PredefinedHandsLoader` → `assets/predefined_hands.yaml`
- Register both in `flutter_base_05/pubspec.yaml` under `flutter: assets:`

### Do not use for Flutter runtime
