## Dart backend (`dart_bkend_base_01`)

### Loading
- `DeckConfig.fromFile('assets/deck_config.yaml')` resolves to **`lib/modules/dutch_game/config/deck_config.yaml`** via `File.readAsString` (`yaml_config_parser.dart`)
- `PredefinedHandsLoader` reads **`lib/modules/dutch_game/config/predefined_hands.yaml`**; missing file → `{enabled: false}`
- Paths are **relative to the server process working directory** (typically `dart_bkend_base_01/` when running the game server). If deck load fails, check cwd matches that layout.

### Implementation (mirror of Flutter shared logic)
- `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/utils/platform/yaml_config_parser.dart`
- `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/utils/platform/predefined_hands_loader.dart`
- `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/backend_core/shared_logic/utils/deck_factory.dart`
- `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/backend_core/coordinator/game_event_coordinator.dart`
- `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/utils/platform/shared_imports.dart` (`DECK_CONFIG_PATH`)

### Backend-only note
- Repo copy of `deck_config.yaml` may ship with `testing_mode: true` for dev — set `false` for production parity with Flutter release builds.

