## Agent checklist

| Task | Flutter | Dart backend |
|------|---------|--------------|
| Change deck composition | `flutter_base_05/assets/deck_config.yaml` | `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/config/deck_config.yaml` |
| Fixed test hands | `flutter_base_05/assets/predefined_hands.yaml` | `dart_bkend_base_01/lib/modules/dutch_game/config/predefined_hands.yaml` |
| Demo / instructions deck | `demo_deck` in both deck YAMLs | same |
| Production | `testing_mode: false`, hands `enabled: false` | same on server YAML |
| Parser / deal bugs | `flutter_base_05/.../yaml_config_parser.dart`, coordinator | `dart_bkend_base_01/.../` equivalents |

- Edit **both** deck YAMLs when changing ranks/powers unless intentionally client-only
- Do not change coordinator deal logic for config tweaks; prefer YAML
- After deck edits: update `deck_stats`, verify predefined ranks exist in active deck section
